=3D"sc-iRTMaw buAyFc"><p>I=E2=80=99m very excited to have participated in t=
his great competition.  <br>
Huge thanks to the organizers and the Kaggle team for hosting such an amazi=
ng challenge. I also want to thank the Kaggle community and fellow particip=
ants for sharing valuable insights, discussions, and notebooks=E2=80=94it w=
as a great opportunity to learn, experiment, and improve my skills.</p>
<p>As someone relatively new to this type of competition, my implementation=
 started from <a href=3D"https://www.kaggle.com/code/octaviograu/baseline-d=
inov2-aliked-lightglue" target=3D"_blank" aria-label=3D"Baseline: DINOV2+AL=
